platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Theres a lot to love in Sago Mini School, but heres the secret ingredient: Its designed in collaboration with leading child development experts. The app offers kids the opportunity to problem-solve and think creatively as they explore topics such as reading, writing, and mathall with the help of Sago Minis signature characters.
